==English==
From Greek '''peri-''' (around) + Greek '''anthos''' (flower).

===Noun===
'''perianth'''
# The sterile parts of a [[flower]]; collectively, the [[sepal]]s and [[petal]]s (or [[tepal]]s).
# The sterile, tubelike tissue that surrounds the female reproductive structure in a leafy [[liverwort]].

